{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1063,"text":"There's an old joke about a cop"},{"time":2602,"text":"who's walking his beat\nin the middle of the night,"},{"time":4983,"text":"and he comes across a guy\nunder a street lamp"},{"time":7110,"text":"who's looking at the ground\nand moving from side to side,"},{"time":9825,"text":"and the cop asks him what he's doing."},{"time":11626,"text":"The guys says he's looking for his keys."},{"time":13584,"text":"So the cop takes his time"},{"time":15047,"text":"and looks over and kind of\nmakes a little matrix"},{"time":17341,"text":"and looks for about two, three minutes."},{"time":19570,"text":"No keys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20745,"text":"The cop says, \"Are you sure?"},{"time":23141,"text":"Hey buddy, are you sure\nyou lost your keys here?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":25474,"text":"And the guy says,\n\"No, actually I lost them"},{"time":27530,"text":"down at the other end of the street,"},{"time":29280,"text":"but the light is better here.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":30749,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34167,"text":"There's a concept that people talk\nabout nowadays called \"big data.\""},{"time":37434,"text":"And what they're talking\nabout is all of the information"},{"time":40101,"text":"that we're generating\nthrough our interaction"},{"time":42276,"text":"with and over the Internet,"},{"time":43603,"text":"everything from Facebook and Twitter"},{"time":45387,"text":"to music downloads, movies,\nstreaming, all this kind of stuff,"},{"time":49044,"text":"the live streaming of TED."},{"time":50919,"text":"And the folks who work\nwith big data, for them,"},{"time":53627,"text":"they talk about that their biggest problem"},{"time":55655,"text":"is we have so much information."},{"time":57426,"text":"The biggest problem is: how do we\norganize all that information?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":61272,"text":"I can tell you that,\nworking in global health,"},{"time":63456,"text":"that is not our biggest problem."},{"time":66232,"text":"Because for us, even though\nthe light is better on the Internet,"},{"time":70989,"text":"the data that would help us solve\nthe problems we're trying to solve"},{"time":74379,"text":"is not actually present on the Internet."},{"time":76552,"text":"So we don't know, for example,"},{"time":78021,"text":"how many people right now\nare being affected by disasters"},{"time":81336,"text":"or by conflict situations."},{"time":83329,"text":"We don't know for, really,\nbasically, any of the clinics"},{"time":87072,"text":"in the developing world,"},{"time":88246,"text":"which ones have medicines\nand which ones don't."},{"time":90725,"text":"We have no idea of what\nthe supply chain is for those clinics."},{"time":94123,"text":"We don't know -- and this is really\namazing to me -- we don't know"},{"time":97845,"text":"how many children were born --\nor how many children there are --"},{"time":101639,"text":"in Bolivia or Botswana or Bhutan."},{"time":106047,"text":"We don't know how many kids died last week"},{"time":108112,"text":"in any of those countries."},{"time":109382,"text":"We don't know the needs\nof the elderly, the mentally ill."},{"time":112453,"text":"For all of these different\ncritically important problems"},{"time":115692,"text":"or critically important areas\nthat we want to solve problems in,"},{"time":119016,"text":"we basically know nothing at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123834,"text":"And part of the reason\nwhy we don't know anything at all"},{"time":126510,"text":"is that the information technology systems\nthat we use in global health"},{"time":130713,"text":"to find the data to solve\nthese problems is what you see here."},{"time":135150,"text":"This is about a 5,000-year-old technology."},{"time":137408,"text":"Some of you may have used it before."},{"time":139164,"text":"It's kind of on its way out now,"},{"time":140727,"text":"but we still use it\nfor 99 percent of our stuff."},{"time":143190,"text":"This is a paper form."},{"time":146010,"text":"And what you're looking at is a paper form"},{"time":148067,"text":"in the hand of a Ministry of Health\nnurse in Indonesia,"},{"time":151270,"text":"who is tramping out across the countryside"},{"time":153534,"text":"in Indonesia on, I'm sure,\na very hot and humid day,"},{"time":157209,"text":"and she is going to be knocking\non thousands of doors"},{"time":159915,"text":"over a period of weeks or months,"},{"time":162018,"text":"knocking on the doors and saying,"},{"time":163639,"text":"\"Excuse me, we'd like to ask\nyou some questions."},{"time":166541,"text":"Do you have any children?\nWere your children vaccinated?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":170223,"text":"Because the only way\nwe can actually find out"},{"time":172382,"text":"how many children were vaccinated\nin the country of Indonesia,"},{"time":175341,"text":"what percentage were vaccinated,"},{"time":176922,"text":"is actually not on the Internet,\nbut by going out and knocking on doors,"},{"time":181074,"text":"sometimes tens of thousands of doors."},{"time":183312,"text":"Sometimes it takes months to even years\nto do something like this."},{"time":187334,"text":"You know, a census of Indonesia"},{"time":189475,"text":"would probably take\ntwo years to accomplish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191593,"text":"And the problem, of course,\nwith all of this"},{"time":193689,"text":"is that, with all those paper forms --"},{"time":195610,"text":"and I'm telling you, we have\npaper forms for every possible thing:"},{"time":198753,"text":"We have paper forms\nfor vaccination surveys."},{"time":200841,"text":"We have paper forms to track\npeople who come into clinics."},{"time":204026,"text":"We have paper forms to track\ndrug supplies, blood supplies --"},{"time":208092,"text":"all these different paper forms\nfor many different topics,"},{"time":211350,"text":"they all have a single, common endpoint,"},{"time":213690,"text":"and the common endpoint\nlooks something like this."},{"time":216333,"text":"And what we're looking\nat here is a truckful of data."},{"time":221261,"text":"This is the data from a single\nvaccination coverage survey"},{"time":225150,"text":"in a single district\nin the country of Zambia"},{"time":227365,"text":"from a few years ago,\nthat I participated in."},{"time":229679,"text":"The only thing anyone\nwas trying to find out"},{"time":232050,"text":"is what percentage of Zambian\nchildren are vaccinated,"},{"time":235327,"text":"and this is the data,\ncollected on paper over weeks,"},{"time":238605,"text":"from a single district,"},{"time":239812,"text":"which is something like a county\nin the United States."},{"time":242511,"text":"You can imagine that,\nfor the entire country of Zambia,"},{"time":245210,"text":"answering just that single question ..."},{"time":248615,"text":"looks something like this."},{"time":251072,"text":"Truck after truck after truck,"},{"time":253136,"text":"filled with stack after stack\nafter stack of data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256430,"text":"And what makes it even worse\nis that's just the beginning."},{"time":259666,"text":"Because once you've collected\nall that data,"},{"time":261784,"text":"of course, someone --\nsome unfortunate person --"},{"time":264348,"text":"is going to have to type that\ninto a computer."},{"time":266587,"text":"When I was a graduate student,"},{"time":268063,"text":"I actually was that unfortunate\nperson sometimes."},{"time":270546,"text":"I can tell you, I often wasn't\nreally paying attention."},{"time":273585,"text":"I probably made a lot\nof mistakes when I did it"},{"time":275876,"text":"that no one ever discovered,\nso data quality goes down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278520,"text":"But eventually that data, hopefully,\ngets typed into a computer,"},{"time":281564,"text":"and someone can begin to analyze it,"},{"time":283319,"text":"and once they have\nan analysis and a report,"},{"time":286215,"text":"hopefully, then you can take\nthe results of that data collection"},{"time":289263,"text":"and use it to vaccinate children better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291254,"text":"Because if there's anything worse\nin the field of global public health --"},{"time":296819,"text":"I don't know what's worse\nthan allowing children on this planet"},{"time":299825,"text":"to die of vaccine-preventable diseases --"},{"time":302679,"text":"diseases for which\nthe vaccine costs a dollar."},{"time":305835,"text":"And millions of children die\nof these diseases every year."},{"time":309211,"text":"And the fact is, millions\nis a gross estimate,"},{"time":312209,"text":"because we don't really know\nhow many kids die each year of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315730,"text":"What makes it even more frustrating\nis that the data-entry part,"},{"time":319253,"text":"the part that I used to do\nas a grad student,"},{"time":321467,"text":"can take sometimes six months."},{"time":322949,"text":"Sometimes it can take two years\nto type that information into a computer,"},{"time":326425,"text":"And sometimes, actually not infrequently,"},{"time":328559,"text":"it actually never happens."},{"time":330411,"text":"Now try and wrap your head\naround that for a second."},{"time":332911,"text":"You just had teams of hundreds of people."},{"time":335110,"text":"They went out into the field\nto answer a particular question."},{"time":338037,"text":"You probably spent hundreds\nof thousands of dollars"},{"time":340457,"text":"on fuel and photocopying and per diem."},{"time":344072,"text":"And then for some reason, momentum is lost"},{"time":346140,"text":"or there's no money left,"},{"time":347557,"text":"and all of that comes to nothing,"},{"time":349918,"text":"because no one actually types it\ninto the computer at all."},{"time":352665,"text":"The process just stops."},{"time":353865,"text":"Happens all the time."},{"time":355813,"text":"This is what we base\nour decisions on in global health:"},{"time":358952,"text":"little data, old data, no data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363924,"text":"So back in 1995,"},{"time":365401,"text":"I began to think about ways\nin which we could improve this process."},{"time":368665,"text":"Now 1995 -- obviously,\nthat was quite a long time ago."},{"time":371357,"text":"It kind of frightens me to think\nof how long ago that was."},{"time":374359,"text":"The top movie of the year\nwas \"Die Hard with a Vengeance.\""},{"time":377121,"text":"As you can see, Bruce Willis\nhad a lot more hair back then."},{"time":379962,"text":"I was working in the Centers\nfor Disease Control"},{"time":382651,"text":"and I had a lot more\nhair back then as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385505,"text":"But to me, the most significant\nthing that I saw in 1995"},{"time":388473,"text":"was this."},{"time":390151,"text":"Hard for us to imagine, but in 1995,"},{"time":392568,"text":"this was the ultimate elite mobile device."},{"time":396286,"text":"It wasn't an iPhone.\nIt wasn't a Galaxy phone."},{"time":398866,"text":"It was a PalmPilot."},{"time":400254,"text":"And when I saw the PalmPilot\nfor the first time, I thought,"},{"time":403806,"text":"\"Why can't we put the forms\non these PalmPilots?"},{"time":406758,"text":"And go out into the field\njust carrying one PalmPilot,"},{"time":409402,"text":"which can hold the capacity\nof tens of thousands of paper forms?"},{"time":413191,"text":"Why don't we try to do that?"},{"time":414642,"text":"Because if we can do that,"},{"time":415929,"text":"if we can actually just collect\nthe data electronically, digitally,"},{"time":419762,"text":"from the very beginning,"},{"time":421443,"text":"we can just put a shortcut right\nthrough that whole process"},{"time":424743,"text":"of typing, of having somebody type\nthat stuff into the computer."},{"time":429759,"text":"We can skip straight to the analysis"},{"time":431623,"text":"and then straight to the use\nof the data to actually save lives.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":434786,"text":"So that's what I began to do."},{"time":437397,"text":"Working at CDC, I began to travel\nto different programs around the world"},{"time":441770,"text":"and to train them in using\nPalmPilots to do data collection,"},{"time":445936,"text":"instead of using paper."},{"time":447338,"text":"And it actually worked great."},{"time":449250,"text":"It worked exactly as well\nas anybody would have predicted."},{"time":452326,"text":"What do you know?"},{"time":453507,"text":"Digital data collection is actually\nmore efficient than collecting on paper."},{"time":457143,"text":"While I was doing it, my business partner,"},{"time":459199,"text":"Rose, who's here with her husband,\nMatthew, here in the audience,"},{"time":462302,"text":"Rose was out doing similar stuff\nfor the American Red Cross."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465199,"text":"The problem was,\nafter a few years of doing that,"},{"time":467609,"text":"I realized -- I had been to maybe\nsix or seven programs --"},{"time":471530,"text":"and I thought, you know,\nif I keep this up at this pace,"},{"time":474815,"text":"over my whole career,"},{"time":475990,"text":"maybe I'm going to go\nto maybe 20 or 30 programs."},{"time":478693,"text":"But the problem is, 20 or 30 programs,"},{"time":481860,"text":"like, training 20 or 30 programs\nto use this technology,"},{"time":484834,"text":"that is a tiny drop in the bucket."},{"time":487024,"text":"The demand for this, the need\nfor data to run better programs"},{"time":490988,"text":"just within health -- not to mention\nall of the other fields"},{"time":493870,"text":"in developing countries -- is enormous."},{"time":495890,"text":"There are millions and millions\nand millions of programs,"},{"time":499900,"text":"millions of clinics\nthat need to track drugs,"},{"time":502492,"text":"millions of vaccine programs."},{"time":503920,"text":"There are schools\nthat need to track attendance."},{"time":506205,"text":"There are all these different things\nfor us to get the data that we need to do."},{"time":510135,"text":"And I realized if I kept up\nthe way that I was doing,"},{"time":514778,"text":"I was basically hardly\ngoing to make any impact"},{"time":518022,"text":"by the end of my career."}]},{"cues":[{"time":519756,"text":"And so I began to rack my brain,"},{"time":521648,"text":"trying to think about, what\nwas the process that I was doing?"},{"time":524616,"text":"How was I training folks,"},{"time":525922,"text":"and what were the bottlenecks\nand what were the obstacles"},{"time":529120,"text":"to doing it faster\nand to doing it more efficiently?"},{"time":531839,"text":"And, unfortunately, after thinking\nabout this for some time,"},{"time":534699,"text":"I identified the main obstacle."},{"time":538475,"text":"And the main obstacle, it turned out --"},{"time":540420,"text":"and this is a sad realization --"},{"time":542032,"text":"the main obstacle was me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544229,"text":"So what do I mean by that?"},{"time":546538,"text":"I had developed a process"},{"time":548278,"text":"whereby I was the center\nof the universe of this technology."},{"time":554304,"text":"If you wanted to use this technology,\nyou had to get in touch with me."},{"time":557651,"text":"That means you had to know I existed."},{"time":559499,"text":"Then you had to find the money\nto pay for me to fly out to your country"},{"time":562936,"text":"and the money to pay for my hotel\nand my per diem and my daily rate."},{"time":566555,"text":"So you could be talking\nabout 10- or 20- or 30,000 dollars,"},{"time":569578,"text":"if I actually had the time\nor it fit my schedule"},{"time":571896,"text":"and I wasn't on vacation."},{"time":573594,"text":"The point is that anything,"},{"time":575579,"text":"any system that depends\non a single human being"},{"time":577966,"text":"or two or three or five human beings --"},{"time":579893,"text":"it just doesn't scale."},{"time":581570,"text":"And this is a problem for which\nwe need to scale this technology,"},{"time":584793,"text":"and we need to scale it now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586387,"text":"And so I began to think of ways\nin which I could basically"},{"time":589165,"text":"take myself out of the picture."},{"time":594071,"text":"And, you know, I was thinking,"},{"time":595739,"text":"\"How could I take myself\nout of the picture?\""},{"time":597867,"text":"for quite some time."},{"time":599510,"text":"I'd been trained that the way\nyou distribute technology"},{"time":603010,"text":"within international development"},{"time":604590,"text":"is always consultant-based."},{"time":606176,"text":"It's always guys\nthat look pretty much like me,"},{"time":609201,"text":"flying from countries\nthat look pretty much like this"},{"time":611773,"text":"to other countries\nwith people with darker skin."},{"time":614769,"text":"And you go out there,\nand you spend money on airfare"},{"time":617255,"text":"and you spend time and you spend per diem"},{"time":620515,"text":"and you spend for a hotel\nand all that stuff."},{"time":622888,"text":"As far as I knew, that was the only way\nyou could distribute technology,"},{"time":626324,"text":"and I couldn't figure out a way around it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628383,"text":"But the miracle that happened --"},{"time":630851,"text":"I'm going to call it Hotmail for short."},{"time":633168,"text":"You may not think of Hotmail\nas being miraculous,"},{"time":635615,"text":"but for me it was miraculous,"},{"time":637076,"text":"because I noticed, just as I\nwas wrestling with this problem --"},{"time":640712,"text":"I was working in sub-Saharan\nAfrica, mostly, at the time --"},{"time":644242,"text":"I noticed that every sub-Saharan\nAfrican health worker"},{"time":646831,"text":"that I was working with\nhad a Hotmail account."},{"time":651389,"text":"And it struck me, \"Wait a minute --"},{"time":654341,"text":"I know the Hotmail people surely didn't\nfly to the Ministry of Health in Kenya"},{"time":658603,"text":"to train people in how to use Hotmail."},{"time":661382,"text":"So these guys are distributing technology,\ngetting software capacity out there,"},{"time":665654,"text":"but they're not actually\nflying around the world."},{"time":668006,"text":"I need to think about this more.\""},{"time":669602,"text":"While I was thinking about it,"},{"time":671076,"text":"people started using even more\nthings like this, just as we were."},{"time":674259,"text":"They started using LinkedIn and Flickr\nand Gmail and Google Maps --"},{"time":677514,"text":"all these things."},{"time":678695,"text":"Of course, all of these things\nare cloud based"},{"time":681410,"text":"and don't require any training."},{"time":683583,"text":"They don't require any programmers."},{"time":685283,"text":"They don't require consultants."},{"time":686810,"text":"Because the business model\nfor all these businesses"},{"time":689319,"text":"requires that something be so simple\nwe can use it ourselves,"},{"time":692280,"text":"with little or no training."},{"time":693598,"text":"You just have to hear about it\nand go to the website."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696217,"text":"And so I thought, what would happen\nif we built software"},{"time":700437,"text":"to do what I'd been consulting in?"},{"time":702525,"text":"Instead of training people\nhow to put forms onto mobile devices,"},{"time":706621,"text":"let's create software that lets them\ndo it themselves with no training"},{"time":709946,"text":"and without me being involved."},{"time":711406,"text":"And that's exactly what we did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712914,"text":"So we created software called Magpi,\nwhich has an online form creator."},{"time":718159,"text":"No one has to speak to me,"},{"time":719435,"text":"you just have to hear about it\nand go to the website."},{"time":722260,"text":"You can create forms,\nand once you've created the forms,"},{"time":724942,"text":"you push them to a variety\nof common mobile phones."},{"time":727427,"text":"Obviously, nowadays, we've moved\npast PalmPilots to mobile phones."},{"time":730968,"text":"And it doesn't have to be a smartphone,\nit can be a basic phone,"},{"time":734221,"text":"like the phone on the right,\nthe basic Symbian phone"},{"time":736735,"text":"that's very common\nin developing countries."},{"time":738821,"text":"And the great part about this\nis it's just like Hotmail."},{"time":742534,"text":"It's cloud based,"},{"time":743709,"text":"and it doesn't require any training,\nprogramming, consultants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746986,"text":"But there are some\nadditional benefits as well."},{"time":749213,"text":"Now we knew when we built this system,"},{"time":751110,"text":"the whole point of it,\njust like with the PalmPilots,"},{"time":753689,"text":"was that you'd be able to collect the data"},{"time":756512,"text":"and immediately upload\nthe data and get your data set."},{"time":759134,"text":"But what we found, of course,\nsince it's already on a computer,"},{"time":762143,"text":"we can deliver instant maps\nand analysis and graphing."},{"time":764778,"text":"We can take a process that took two years"},{"time":766873,"text":"and compress that\ndown to the space of five minutes."},{"time":770222,"text":"Unbelievable improvements in efficiency."},{"time":772740,"text":"Cloud based, no training,\nno consultants, no me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777520,"text":"And I told you that in the first few years"},{"time":779815,"text":"of trying to do this\nthe old-fashioned way,"},{"time":781908,"text":"going out to each country,"},{"time":783211,"text":"we probably trained about 1,000 people."},{"time":787871,"text":"What happened after we did this?"},{"time":789577,"text":"In the second three years,"},{"time":791062,"text":"we had 14,000 people find the website,"},{"time":793236,"text":"sign up and start using it\nto collect data:"},{"time":795373,"text":"data for disaster response,"},{"time":797307,"text":"Canadian pig farmers\ntracking pig disease and pig herds,"},{"time":801765,"text":"people tracking drug supplies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804241,"text":"One of my favorite examples, the IRC,\nInternational Rescue Committee,"},{"time":807609,"text":"they have a program\nwhere semi-literate midwives,"},{"time":810846,"text":"using $10 mobile phones,"},{"time":813273,"text":"send a text message\nusing our software, once a week,"},{"time":816598,"text":"with the number of births\nand the number of deaths,"},{"time":819098,"text":"which gives IRC something that no one\nin global health has ever had:"},{"time":822694,"text":"a near-real-time system\nof counting babies,"},{"time":826240,"text":"of knowing how many kids are born,"},{"time":827898,"text":"of knowing how many children\nthere are in Sierra Leone,"},{"time":830564,"text":"which is the country\nwhere this is happening,"},{"time":832811,"text":"and knowing how many children die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835394,"text":"Physicians for Human Rights --"},{"time":836991,"text":"this is moving a little bit\noutside the health field --"},{"time":839607,"text":"they're basically training people\nto do rape exams in Congo,"},{"time":844414,"text":"where this is an epidemic,"},{"time":845887,"text":"a horrible epidemic,"},{"time":847704,"text":"and they're using our software\nto document the evidence they find,"},{"time":850904,"text":"including photographically,"},{"time":852902,"text":"so that they can bring\nthe perpetrators to justice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856956,"text":"Camfed, another charity\nbased out of the UK --"},{"time":860573,"text":"Camfed pays girls' families\nto keep them in school."},{"time":864165,"text":"They understand this is the most\nsignificant intervention they can make."},{"time":867664,"text":"They used to track the disbursements,\nthe attendance, the grades, on paper."},{"time":871528,"text":"The turnaround time between a teacher\nwriting down grades or attendance"},{"time":874899,"text":"and getting that into a report\nwas about two to three years."},{"time":877758,"text":"Now it's real time."},{"time":878933,"text":"And because this is such a low-cost\nsystem and based in the cloud,"},{"time":882140,"text":"it costs, for the entire five countries\nthat Camfed runs this in,"},{"time":886153,"text":"with tens of thousands of girls,"},{"time":888042,"text":"the whole cost combined\nis 10,000 dollars a year."},{"time":891154,"text":"That's less than I used to get"},{"time":893139,"text":"just traveling out for two weeks\nto do a consultation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898139,"text":"So I told you before that when\nwe were doing it the old-fashioned way,"},{"time":901632,"text":"I realized all of our work was really\nadding up to just a drop in the bucket --"},{"time":905451,"text":"10, 20, 30 different programs."},{"time":908036,"text":"We've made a lot of progress,"},{"time":909473,"text":"but I recognize that right now,"},{"time":911053,"text":"even the work that we've done\nwith 14,000 people using this"},{"time":914441,"text":"is still a drop in the bucket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":915928,"text":"But something's changed,\nand I think it should be obvious."},{"time":918682,"text":"What's changed now is,"},{"time":920861,"text":"instead of having a program\nin which we're scaling at such a slow rate"},{"time":924187,"text":"that we can never reach\nall the people who need us,"},{"time":927522,"text":"we've made it unnecessary\nfor people to get reached by us."},{"time":931128,"text":"We've created a tool\nthat lets programs keep kids in school,"},{"time":936155,"text":"track the number of babies that are born\nand the number of babies that die,"},{"time":940118,"text":"catch criminals and successfully\nprosecute them --"},{"time":943919,"text":"to do all these different things\nto learn more about what's going on,"},{"time":948365,"text":"to understand more,"},{"time":949690,"text":"to see more ..."},{"time":951911,"text":"and to save lives and improve lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":955920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":957096,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}